## About this event

****Join Us for an Exclusive Entrepreneur Event: From Post to Profit — DBBC’s Entrepreneur Marketing Panel****

Each year, The Denver Boss Babe Collective hosts a highly anticipated panel happy hour event featuring experts who directly support local entrepreneurs. This year, we’re thrilled to spotlight a powerhouse lineup of DBBC members who can help you take your small business marketing **from post to profit**.

You’ll hear from:

The event will be held at the vibrant, woman- and LGBTQ-owned ****Town Hall Collaborative****. Your ticket includes your first drink from Town Hall’s artistic menu, and snack boxes (available by pre-order) will be curated by DBBC’s own ****Yukari Bianchi****, owner of UNI Personal Chefs.

✨ **This is our only event of the year that’s open to the public** — so whether you’re a member or not, grab your spot! Seats are limited and will go fast.

We can’t wait to welcome you to an inspiring and actionable evening of connection and expertise.

**Tickets for this event may be refunded up to 7 days prior to August 27, 2025 via Eventbrite. Tickets will be sold until noon on August 27, 2025, or until the event is sold out; whichever comes first.** *****NOTE: Snack box orders will stop on August 19, 2025.*******Tickets for DBBC events normally sell out many days before the event date. Due to the price point uniqueness of each monthly event, tickets are NON-transferable for future DBBC events.**
